Invocation Name: pure f. m. london
des: Welcome to Pure FM London, your premier destination for the finest sounds of the underground. Launched in 2022, Pure FM has quickly become a cornerstone of the UK music scene, celebrating the rich history and evolution of underground House, Garage, Jungle, Drum and Bass, and beyond. Broadcasting straight from the heart of London, our mission is simple: to provide a platform for the freshest underground beats, showcase cutting-edge talent, and connect listeners to the pulse of the city’s thriving music culture. Whether you’re a lifelong raver or a new explorer of the underground, Pure FM brings you the sounds that matter.
